					<h2>Results</h2>

<div id="result" class="result-section" style="display: none;">
	
	<p >Estimated Due Date: <span id="dueDateResult"></span></p>
	<p >Current Week of Pregnancy: <span id="weekResult"></span></p>
</div>
	
